&lt;p&gt;I would say this issue is critical, as if it occurs, the node will crash on commitlog replay, too (if it was restarted for unrelated reason). &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However, the fix is relatively simple: check for static clustering in &lt;tt&gt;ColumnIndex&lt;/tt&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;cc &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=xedin&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;xedin&quot;&gt;xedin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
